3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with the development of an intelligent system for object recognition. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper proposes a deep learning network that uses neural networks for image classification. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with the processing and analysis of image datasets.
